\s1 Yahweh said he disapproved of what Job’s three friends said  
\p
\v 7 \w After|strong="H1961"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w these|strong="H1696"\w* \w things|strong="H1697"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w Job|strong="H3808"\w*, \w he|strong="H3588"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* Eliphaz, “\w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w am|strong="H1961"\w* \w angry|strong="H2734"\w* \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* \w two|strong="H8147"\w* \w friends|strong="H7453"\w*, \add Bildad and Zophar\add*, \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w what|strong="H1697"\w* \w my|strong="H3068"\w* \w servant|strong="H5650"\w* \w Job|strong="H3808"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w about|strong="H1961"\w* \w me|strong="H1696"\w* \w was|strong="H3068"\w* \w right|strong="H3559"\w*/\w true|strong="H3068"\w*, \w but|strong="H3588"\w* \w what|strong="H1697"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w have|strong="H1961"\w* \w spoken|strong="H1696"\w* \w about|strong="H1961"\w* \w me|strong="H1696"\w* \w was|strong="H3068"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w right|strong="H3559"\w*/\w true|strong="H3068"\w*.  
\v 8 \w So|strong="H6213"\w* \w now|strong="H6258"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w must|strong="H3947"\w* \w take|strong="H3947"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w Job|strong="H3808"\w* \w seven|strong="H7651"\w* \w young|strong="H6499"\w* \w bulls|strong="H6499"\w* \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w seven|strong="H7651"\w* rams \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \add kill them and\add* \w burn|strong="H5927"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* altar \w as|strong="H6213"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w sacrifice|strong="H5930"\w* \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w yourselves|strong="H5921"\w*. \w Then|strong="H1696"\w* \w Job|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H5650"\w* \w pray|strong="H6419"\w* \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w*, \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H5650"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w what|strong="H6213"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* requests \w me|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w*, \add and I will forgive you for speaking wrongly about me\add*. \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H5650"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w punish|strong="H6213"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w*, \w even|strong="H3588"\w* \w though|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* deserve \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* punished, \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w what|strong="H6213"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w about|strong="H5921"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w* \w was|strong="H5650"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w right|strong="H3559"\w*/true, \w but|strong="H3588"\w* \w what|strong="H6213"\w* \w Job|strong="H3808"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w about|strong="H5921"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w* \w was|strong="H5650"\w* \w right|strong="H3559"\w*/true.”   
\p
\v 9 \w So|strong="H6213"\w* Eliphaz, \w Bildad|strong="H1085"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w Zophar|strong="H6691"\w* \w did|strong="H6213"\w* \w what|strong="H6213"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w commanded|strong="H1696"\w* \w them|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w did|strong="H6213"\w* \w what|strong="H6213"\w* \w Job|strong="H6440"\w* requested \w him|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \add for the three of them\add*.   
\s1 Yahweh blessed Job again  
